  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You wake up in a basement after being kidnapped. As you search for a way out, you figure out that something terrible happened here just recently.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Find a way to escape</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the basement, search for a way out. But something will try to keep you inside.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285930/extras/9e181208dd55ce9b2402ac1e87e4f0cf.poster.avif?t=1747051322\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285930/extras/9e181208dd55ce9b2402ac1e87e4f0cf.webm?t=1747051322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285930/extras/9e181208dd55ce9b2402ac1e87e4f0cf.mp4?t=1747051322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You are not alone</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Something is always nearby, and if you see it, find a place to hide or run to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285930/extras/f09df9095945cca157cd4e083c1eac54.poster.avif?t=1747051322\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285930/extras/f09df9095945cca157cd4e083c1eac54.webm?t=1747051322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285930/extras/f09df9095945cca157cd4e083c1eac54.mp4?t=1747051322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Secrets and puzzles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve puzzles, discover secrets, and piece together the story of what happened here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285930/extras/e38ae12b11875de693884352eb39b736.poster.avif?t=1747051322\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285930/extras/e38ae12b11875de693884352eb39b736.webm?t=1747051322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285930/extras/e38ae12b11875de693884352eb39b736.mp4?t=1747051322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two main endings and one secret ending.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Approximate playtime: 20-40 minutes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Primarily a first-person walking simulator.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
